# 🌿 Leaf Ltd — Business Management System

REST API built with Spring Boot 3.3.4 + Java 21 for managing employee attendance, delivery sheets, and warehouse damaged products.

## 📋 Modules
- ✅ JWT Authentication with role-based access (BOSS, OFFICE, MANAGER, EMPLOYEE)
- ✅ Employee attendance control (check-in / check-out)
- ✅ Delivery sheet management
- ✅ Damaged products registry
- ✅ Employee and user CRUD

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Java 21
- Spring Boot 3.3.4
- Spring Security + JWT (jjwt 0.11.5)
- PostgreSQL
- Spring Data JPA / Hibernate
- Swagger / OpenAPI 2.6.0
- Lombok

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Java 21
- Maven 3.8+
- PostgreSQL 14+

### Installation

1. Clone the repository
```bash
   git clone https://github.com/kevinbarrios22/leaf-ltd.git
   cd leaf-ltd
```

2. Create the PostgreSQL database
```sql
   CREATE DATABASE leafltd;
```

3. Configure the application
```bash
   cp src/main/resources/application.yml.example src/main/resources/application.yml
```
   Edit `application.yml` with your database credentials and JWT secret.

4. Run the application
```bash
   mvn spring-boot:run
```

5. Open Swagger UI